## Product Categories & Subcategories

### 1. Axles

Individual trailer axles sold by weight rating. All axles come with spring pads pre-welded, hubs installed, and are available in idler (no brakes), electric brake, or hydraulic brake configurations.

| Weight Rating | Tube Diameter | Typical Bolt Pattern | Common Use |
|---|---|---|---|
| 3,500 lbs | 2-3/8" round | 5 lug (4.5" or 4.75") | Utility, boat, small cargo |
| 5,200 lbs | 3" round | 6 lug (5.5") | Medium utility, car hauler |
| 6,000 lbs | 3" round | 6 lug (5.5") | Medium duty cargo, landscape |
| 7,000 lbs | 3" round | 8 lug (6.5") | Car hauler, equipment, flatbed |
| 8,000 lbs | 3" round | 8 lug (6.5") | Heavy cargo, equipment |
| 10,000 lbs | 3.5" round | 8 lug (6.5") | Gooseneck, heavy equipment |
| 12,000 lbs | 3.5"–4" round | 8 lug (6.5") | Heavy commercial, gooseneck |
| 16,000 lbs | 5" round | 8 lug (6.5") | Extreme heavy duty |

**Brake types offered**: Idler (no brake), Electric drum, Hydraulic drum, Hydraulic disc

**Grease options**: EZ-Lube (grease), Oil bath

### 2. Trailer Axle Kits

Complete package deals that include axle(s), springs, hangers, U-bolts, and sometimes tires/wheels. Sold as ready-to-install bundles.

- **Single Axle Kits**: 3.5k, 5.2k, 6k, 7k, 8k, 10k, 12k
- **Tandem Axle Kits**: 3.5k (7k GVWR), 5.2k (10.4k GVWR), 6k (12k GVWR), 7k (14k GVWR), 8k (16k GVWR), 10k (20k GVWR), 12k (24k GVWR)
- **Triple Axle Kits**: 3.5k (10.5k GVWR), 7k (21k GVWR), 8k (24k GVWR), 10k (30k GVWR), 12k (36k GVWR)

**Kit typically includes**: Axle(s), leaf springs (double eye or slipper), hanger kit (weld-on), U-bolt kit, equalizer(s) for tandem/triple. Some kits also bundle tires and wheels.

### 3. Trailer Suspension

All components needed to build or repair trailer suspension systems.

- **Bolts & Nuts**: Equalizer bolts, lock nuts (3/4", 7/8", 1", 1-1/8"), shackle bolts (greaseable and standard), spring eye bolts
- **Bushings**: Nylon spring bushings (for 1-3/4" and 2" wide leaf springs), bronze bushings
- **Hangers, Equalizers & Hardware**: Front hangers, rear hangers, center hangers, equalizers, spring shackle straps/link plates, hanger kits (single, tandem, triple)
- **Spring Pads**: Weld-on pads for 2-3/8", 3", 3.5" round axle tubes
- **Suspension Kits**: Complete single-axle and tandem-axle suspension packages (hangers + springs + hardware)
- **U-Bolts & Kits**: Square and round U-bolts for 2-3/8", 3", 3.5" axle tubes; tie plates included in kits
- **Leaf Springs**: Double-eye springs (1-3/4" and 2" wide), slipper springs (2" and 2-1/2" wide), available in 3–7 leaf configurations for various weight ratings
- **Shackle Straps**: Link plates for connecting double-eye springs to hangers/equalizers
- **Air Springs / Air Suspension Bags**: Aftermarket air-ride kits for heavy-duty trailers
- **Hutch Suspension**: HDSS (Heavy Duty Spring Suspension) 9700 Series weld-on kits for 10k–16k axles; tandem and triple configurations

