### 5. Trailer Axle Parts

Replacement and maintenance parts for trailer axles.

- **Axle End Units**: Complete spindle/hub/brake assemblies
- **Brake Calipers**: Hydraulic disc brake calipers for 10k–12k axles; bleeder screws
- **Brake Magnets**: Electric brake magnets for various axle ratings
- **Oil & Grease Caps**: Dust caps, oil bath caps, rubber plugs (EZ-Lube and oil bath)
- **Trailer Brakes**: Electric drum brake assemblies (LH/RH), hydraulic drum brakes, hydraulic disc brakes; brake mounting hardware (bolts, nuts, lock washers)
- **Hubs & Drums**: Hub/drum combos for 3.5k–16k axles; various lug counts and bolt patterns; pre-greased options with bearings installed
- **Spindles & Hardware**: Replacement spindles, spindle nuts (castle nuts), spindle washers (round and D-shaped/tang), cotter pins
- **Bearings, Races, Seals & Kits**: Inner/outer bearing sets, bearing races, grease seals, oil seals; complete bearing kits by axle rating
- **Wheel Studs & Lug Nuts**: 1/2"-20, 9/16"-18, 5/8"-18 studs and matching cone lug nuts
- **Spring Seats / Spring Pads**: Weld-on spring seats for various tube diameters
- **Caps & Seals**: Grease caps, oil bath caps, hub seals

**Repair Kits**: Complete axle repair kits for Dexter-compatible 9–10k axles (hydraulic drum), available for pre-7/2009 and post-7/2009 spindle designs.

### 6. Trailer Lights

LED lighting for trailers, trucks, and commercial vehicles.

- **Clearance Lights**: Amber and red LED side marker lights; rectangular and round; surface mount and grommet mount
- **Emergency Strobe Lights**: 4" round and 6" oval amber/red LED strobe/flashing lights
- **License-Plate Lights & Mounting Brackets**: LED license plate illumination
- **Light Boxes**: Steel light boxes for mounting tail lights
- **Stop, Turn, Tail & Back-up Lights**: 4" round and 6" oval red LED stop/turn/tail combos; clear LED reverse/back-up lights; with 3-prong plugs and rubber grommets
- **Trailer Light Kits**: Complete wiring + light packages for trailers
- **Work Light Bars**: LED work lights (e.g., 4" 72W spot/flood combo bars, 12V/24V)

**Common specs**: 10–24 LED count, 12V/24V compatible, DOT-compliant, waterproof with rubber grommets and sealed connectors

