## Content & SEO Notes

- TPU primarily serves the **DIY trailer builder** and **trailer repair** market
- Customers range from homeowners building small utility trailers to commercial fleet operators
- Popular blog topics: tire comparisons (ST235/85R16 vs 235/75R17.5), bolt pattern measurement guides, Hutch HDSS suspension benefits
- All axle products emphasize **Dexter-compatible / Dexter-interchangeable** design
- Carter brand products are manufactured to be direct replacements for Dexter and Lippert components
- Price range spans from $0.15 (cotter pin) to $8,347+ (complete 24k tandem kits)
- Shipping is calculated at checkout based on zip code; heavy items ship via LTL freight
